::Dollen::

         Dollen rubbed his head, trying to forget the dream.

         After resting for a few minutes, he got up, and decided to head
back to base.

        He went to open his com to GoldenEye, but just then, GoldenEye
opened her com to him.

       He gave a slight laugh.

       "I'm not too far away from where you are, love.  If the commander
wants to know, I'll be back in a flash.  See ya!" He said, and with that, he
transformed into taranturtle mode, and scuttled off for the base.
